    "priority": [
      "High"
    ]
  }
}
\`\`\`
Expected Output: High-priority bugs linked to step 1

3. Filter by status
\`\`\`json
{
  "testCycleKey": "PROJ-TR-101",
  "testCaseKey": "PROJ-TC-42",
